In this Order, “United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland”

title: Act 2015 (No. 66 of 2015) (as adapted by the Justice and Equality (Alteration of
heading: 3. The United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland is designated
text_raw:
3. The United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland is designated 
as a safe third country for the purposes of the International Protection Act 2015 
(No. 66 of 2015). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

11 March, 2025. 

JIM O’CALLAGHAN, 
Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 14th March, 2025.
